{"tid":2180692,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有幾多人仲同緊屋企人一齊住?","createTime":"2020-08-30T04:58:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T04:50:43.000Z","uid":64576,"like":149,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"0b330b91aebacc201ddb3136da8155583d74b918","tid":2180692,"uid":64576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T04:58:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fsq_BLf6Qwk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ffsq_BLf6Qwk&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLOdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=0a394d90\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fsq_BLf6Qwk</a><br />\n喺youtube睇果籽<br />\n見到啲日本仔日本妹每個月搵萬幾蚊都搬咗岀嚟住<br />\n仲要個租金都已經佔咗月入嘅三分之一至一半咁濟<br />\n不過好好彩嘅係佢哋間房個間隔都好正<br />\n同埋日本去超市買嘢應該會平過香港<br />\n<br />\n同樣喺香港 大家都知道喺市區租一個100呎左右嘅劏房至少都要5000蚊 日常去超市買嘢個價都係好貴  另外香港樓價世界第一 同埋大學生咁多年起薪都差唔多 令到好多人宜家仲同緊屋企人住緊<br />\n<br />\n到底有幾多人25歲以上仲同緊屋企人? <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲同緊屋企人住<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已經搬咗岀去<br />\n<br />\n利申26 仲同緊屋企人住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd76cf71dd44d85a01cb05286216e395d0508bc7","tid":2180692,"uid":70634,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T04:59:11.000Z","msg":"25公屋仔同緊屋企住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd0f36aefe92db19bce08c1be430cbf8caaa72f7","tid":2180692,"uid":155818,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T04:59:29.000Z","msg":"試過出去住<br />\n真係儲唔到錢<br />\n痴老母算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a8bf9e55fb46559c60c96daa60ea61970026d3","tid":2180692,"uid":258683,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T05:01:15.000Z","msg":"就3張野 同屋企人住<br />\n家庭和睦 無理由搬出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f3e531ac0e6455aee5d102e115c4e320f